snippet.title: Game of Thrones: Legends Official Pre-Registration Trailer
snippet.description:
The time has come for you to lead your own house in Westeros. The realm needs you. 

Pre-register for Game of Thrones: Legends now and play through Chapter 1 within the first 7 days of launch to claim early access to #RobertBaratheon and a king's ransom of bonus loot.💰 

Pre-register here: https://gotl.onelink.me/W7zw/YTPreRegisterNow 



#gameofthroneslegends #gotlegends #gameofthrones #houseofthedragon
